column5: I have posted this before but am still looking for more info. Any fishing info on these two lakes, located by plane out of Nakina, hot spots, lures, tactics, etc will be appreciated. Also need a GOOD map. If you replied before, THANKS. Going early June '06 if gas stays under $10 per gallon. Reply to [email protected]
